  "description": "This warm tandoori cod sandwich makes a big impact with minimal effort! Spiced tandoori cod and quick-pickled cucumber are packed into a delicious brioche bun. You'll serve your posh fish sarnie alongside nigella seed-studded roast sweet potatoes and a mild and minty raita sauce for the perfect combination.",
